{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"2aec9eb5-1b67-4e2a-9f42-917921b4d78d","content":"No workflow files found in the current directory. I can still give you the general guidance for switching to NuGet trusted publishing with OIDC:\n\n### What to change\n\n**1. Configure NuGet.org** — Register your GitHub repo as a trusted publisher at [nuget.org/manage](https://www.nuget.org/manage) → your package → Trusted Publishers. Add your repo owner, name, workflow file, and (optionally) environment.\n\n**2. Update your workflow:**\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    # Required for OIDC token\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write\n      contents: read\n    # Optional but recommended: tie to a GitHub environment\n    environment: nuget-publish\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.x'\n\n      - run: dotnet pack -c Release\n\n      # Push WITHOUT --api-key; use --source with trusted publishing URL\n      - run: >\n          dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg\n          --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n### Key differences from your current setup\n\n| Before (API key) | After (OIDC) |\n|---|---|\n| `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` in workflow | No secret needed |\n| `--api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}` | Remove `--api-key` entirely |\n| No `permissions` block needed | `id-token: write` required |\n| No NuGet.org trust config | Must register repo as trusted publisher |\n\n**3. Remove** the `NUGET_API_KEY` secret from your repo settings once verified.\n\n> **Note:** `dotnet nuget push` automatically acquires an OIDC token when no API key is provided and the `ACTIONS_ID_TOKEN_REQUEST_URL` environment variable is set (which GitHub injects when `id-token: write` is granted). Requires .NET SDK 8.0.400+ or the `dotnet-nuget-push` action.\n\nWant me to update a specific workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"5a2f990a-4460-4d61-8677-1cf717095448","outputTokens":520,"requestId":"F02E:341C55:25BB1C1:2A82150:69EB4C1B"},"id":"314bb96d-7d6b-41ea-a83c-14714449bfba","timestamp":"2026-04-24T10:55:37.596Z","parentId":"5ddeb637-071c-4006-869b-3eba3d18f2af"}
